  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_6349e417ec876b0f689a6aea3541685b">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>This collection documents Vijay Nambisan's literary life and his marriage to Kavery Nambisan, herself a novelist and surgeon.  It contains correspondence, clippings, drafts of poetry and prose, notebooks and diaries, paintings and illustrations.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_c19348fa048896583e724b037f8a30d3">
    <head>Preferred Citation</head>
<p>Vijay Nambisan papers, #8693. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_eca07e6171c5659e27bb424784cdec42">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Vijay Nambisan was a poet, journalist, critic and writer of non-fiction, with three collections of poetry, three books of non-fiction and dozens of essays.</p>  </bioghist>
